OL,4,G0005F999: On the Front Line
OL,5,     GParamedics treat a woman with a
OL,6,     Gpossible bleed on the brain, a
OL,7,     Gbaby whose heart is beating
OL,8,     Gextremely fast, a man showing
OL,9,     Gsigns of a stroke, and a woman
OL,10,     Gwho may have sepsis.
OL,11,G0110F24 Hours in A&E
OL,12,     GThis episode meets people who've
OL,13,     Gtaken big risks and explores how
OL,14,     Git's affected their lives.
OL,15,     GMotorbikers James and Peter are
OL,16,     Gboth rushed in. Ex-miner Alfred
OL,17,     Ghas severe chest pain.
